Okhulumela amaphoyisa KwaZulu-Natal, uColonel Thembeka Mbele, uthe amaphoyisa ophiko olulwa noDlame lweMindeni, ukuVikelwa kweziNgane namaCala oCansi aphenye amacala abamangalelwa. Kwabawu-15 abalahlwe ngamacala kukhona abathole odilikajele. “Bane odilikajele abakhishiwe neminyaka ewu- 247. Abamangalelwa bagwetshwe ezinkantolo ezehlukene zesifundazwe,” kusho uColonel Mbele. Uthe omunye wabalahlwe ngamacala ugwetshwe odilikajele abathathu kanti oyedwa uthole udilikajele owodwa. Abanye basahamba amacala ezinkantolo ezehlukene.